{"tid":748201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[QR關又柒一鑊] 首次引入Tap ＆ Go QR Code賣書 現場實試方唔方便","createTime":"2018-07-19T04:29:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-22T14:32:47.000Z","uid":1159,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"68bf3cf1c2fbff5cb112e39c4d9c1baf05685b1e","tid":748201,"uid":1159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T04:29:04.000Z","msg":"按：Tap &amp; Go為HKT Payment 旗下之支付服務，即係大老闆係李澤楷<br />\n<br />\n【書展2018】首次引入Tap ＆ Go賣書 現場實試方唔方便<br />\n<br />\n每年書展排隊入場和買書，相信大家都會覺得很累，如果不用排隊，或能縮短等候時間該多好！大概有見及此，Tap &amp; Go於今年書展2018推出Virtual Store，即場掃瞄QR code即可用Tap &amp; Go手機錢包付款買書，讓大家不用逐個攤位排隊，體驗購物的便利。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180719/large/19sub365new1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180719%2Flarge%2F19sub365new1.jpg&h=00a882d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTap &amp; Go在書展的1B出口設立了兩個大屏幕，供市民掃描QR Code買書。<br />\n<br />\n在書展的出口和Tap &amp; Go的攤位，都有Virtual Store讓用家掃瞄QR code購物，只要用一般QR Code掃瞄App掃一下，就會自動進入購買頁面，之後的過程和一般網上購物類似，可選擇購買的物品和數量，也可再掃描更多產品並加進購物車，之後可選擇即場提取或免費送貨上門，最後付款時就會直接轉至Tap &amp; Go付款，整個過程不用一分鐘。現場提取，只要在出口的Tap &amp; Go提貨攤位等一會，就有專人運送過來。除了快捷方便外，部分商品更有Tap &amp; Go優惠價，可惜的是這個方便實惠的購物方法，只提供37件產品可供選購。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180719/large/19sub365new2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180719%2Flarge%2F19sub365new2.jpg&h=8e27853b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n購買後可選擇於現場提取，或送貨上門。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180719/large/19sub365new3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180719%2Flarge%2F19sub365new3.jpg&h=428d85a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTap &amp; Go App可直接購買書展電子門票，不用花時間排隊買門票。<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提，書展現場設有Tap &amp; Go增值服務，另外，還可以透過Tap &amp; Go購買書展電子門票，可省卻排隊買入場券時間。<br />\n<br />\n記者：馬子聰、梁志穎<br />\n攝影：徐振國<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/tech/daily/article/20180719/20453759\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Ftech%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180719%2F20453759&d=ffeL2UZe1D0zqWnfAH%2BT1QRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=353ddbf6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Ftech%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180719%2F20453759&h=bfac7dba\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/tech/daily/article/20180719/20453759</a>"},{"pid":"048f69ed561b148d7b76a8b803f3e86bb10a06b5","tid":748201,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T04:31:00.000Z","msg":"tap n go 當MasterCard用<br />\nQR 咁柒煩，不了"},{"pid":"0ddaa389997d73c6f5a077856d68835ee4c5565f","tid":748201,"uid":107936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T14:32:47.000Z","msg":"On撚9 又成日壞"}]}